_:N4d9c3c59e2cf41bebed832e86fcc083c <http://schema.org/description> "The Livestock and Meat Commission for Northern Ireland (LMC) is an Executive Non-Departmental Public Body, which was established by Statute (The Livestock Marketing Commission Act [Northern Ireland] 1967) to assist the development of the livestock and livestock products industries. LMC (NI) is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Department of Agriculture, Environment and Rural Affairs (Northern Ireland) ." .
